# gen52: the ELIMINATION move. A single contentless word as the very first turn,
# claimed by no content module, is by exclusion a phatic contact act -- so a
# NOVEL opener parrot0 never listed ("ahoy") is still handled, with an opening
# that invites content (honest: it does not feign understanding). This is
# structure (form + discourse position), not a bigger greeting list.
> ahoy
< Hi there! What would you like to talk about?
